summary: REQ-8 and REQ-9 appear implemented by updating the header logo src/alt in MauiAppShell and updating the favicon link in frontend/index.html. However, the diff shows no newly added/generated image assets under frontend/public/assets/generated, so REQ-6 and REQ-7 are not satisfied. Additionally, non-requested metadata/state files were modified.
